Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.48,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.82,0:00:29.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.62,0:00:39.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都着着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:47.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.11,0:00:57.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:13.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会因为这种事而惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不会高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正里头一定是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.07,0:01:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的钞票吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失主给我两千元当作谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.62,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生什么好事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是某种巨大灾难的前兆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第十话  悲伤你好」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演是班长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.69,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大道具是若宫、照明是森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音响则是泷川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生抽蓝色 女生抽红色的签
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽到一号的是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王是濑户口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想当国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要一下子就死的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是角色是公平抽签的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合我的角色只有勇敢的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.17,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上公主的绅士英雄非我莫属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让芳野老师困扰的学生 我绝对不会原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么二号是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须是坏魔法师对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是抽到二号吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词太多了 我想当后台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是来须…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让芳野老师哭泣的学生 就由我来对付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有点累了 善行 交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来六号是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是望望美 望望美抽到六号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.14,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美当妖精啊 这很合适呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就不用问了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号公主是芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八号侍女一定是田边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号是芝村是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是八号的侍女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤 出这种错真不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么忘记把公主的签放进去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我好像不小心做两个侍女的签了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么一回事吧 田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天起也要戴眼镜了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有视力我很有自信的说\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(七号 公主)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得忐忑不安呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边该不会发生什么大事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.38,0:05:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们部队要担任PBE任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动助理会是田边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟她已经实习结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姊只是杞人忧天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边现在会这样 只是以前的反作用力罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看田边真纪这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的不幸可不是普通的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.84,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边得到担任公主 演女主角这种小小幸福的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会遭遇恐怖的灾难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么认真在说 还真恐怖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算用这台来拍田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍录影带？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坏的状况 田边可能会挂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时把这卷「最后的英姿」寄给她家人 不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.57,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上有些玩笑是不能开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊 怎么用我的腔调讲话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你这么不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么不幸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 这个字要怎么念？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为毁灭的我叹息而流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你这么不幸 竟然还为毁灭的我叹息而流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于公主的美远近驰名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了见公主一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大厅聚集了王宫贵族及骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位今天来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主如今亭亭玉立 如今只需要找个好女婿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宫呢 他不是负责大道具吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是还担任旁白吗 要等念完台词才会来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身体撑得住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心那个笨蛋壮牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况需要担心的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要担心的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来须
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.01,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是庆祝之宴 你为何而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来是为了告诉各位一则预言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.46,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了来宣告死亡 夺走一切的希望而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了 悲哀土地的后裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等的土地将世代受到谄咒 水将会变得腐烂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须他只要讲太多话 好像就会不舒服的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的帅哥 为什么要戴胡子当老头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是不顺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是当佣人而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 你很高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小志、小隆、小阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞的衣服也作好啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小志是一组的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要彩排了 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定中仆人跟侍女是夫妇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水 你其实很高兴对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今国王跟皇后已经过世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今公主已经浪迹天涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.88,0:09:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这宽广严苛的世界里 公主能够依靠的只有我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算你这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.76,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是恐怖的魔法师 我们根本不是他的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是选错角色了吧\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你也看到了吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女看起来比较有气质呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(军队一瞬间就化为灰烬)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得啊\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我当然看到啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.14,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边当起公主也不错呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我们只擅长做饭跟铺床)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没办法挥剑作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的其实也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.28,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被懦弱附身的仆人夫妇抛弃公主而自己逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 黑夜过去 清晨来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉的云覆盖着大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是恶灵作崇吗 还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位美丽的女性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道身分相当高贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE活性化成功！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我搞错了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吃个饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是选错角色了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟远坂对戏时 你好像很不自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也知道 虽然知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论如何身体都会僵硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…难道对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 你对远坂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会笑你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对大家保守秘密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说出来的 只会藏在心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村愿意听我说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在去年的四月 樱花开始绽放的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.25,0:12:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是一年最美的季节 春天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有十元铜板而困扰的我 面前出现上天派来的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮丽的黑发、清澈的墨绿眼睛 温柔且温暖的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.38,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人想起古代希腊的雕刻 那位面容尊贵的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样从我的面前离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个古代希腊什么的是远坂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打了一通电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尚敬高中吗 请帮我转接5121部队整备小组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起对不起 我是田边 真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 那是汽油车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的两个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中都是那个人的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在上学的第一天 我知道他是同个部队的学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴 真的好感谢神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.73,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你们是男女主角 加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加练习 一定就会变得自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.24,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村 我可以问一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村对速水没什么感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么是指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说就是喜欢之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此吧 我是这么确信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.09,0:13:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我还是说出来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.26,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水不是都有点懦弱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那种的不适合芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.78,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.48,0:14:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合芝村的必须像男子汉 而且还要有包容力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像速水那样的人不适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也不是这么不值得一提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他其实也有像男人的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能很难相信 但却是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连一开始的我都不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 我们来练习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间已经不够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了 马上就会开演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急广播、紧急广播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇土地区出现幻兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队尽速准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次 5121部队尽速准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我们等多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不开始吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位先听我说一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊你又要说冷笑话了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想说有可能这样 所以我已经先编辑好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是加藤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(坏魔法师跟最后的王国)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很久以前的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一座小小的王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王国的人民都勤朴俭实 过着相当幸福的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔性之人 这里是庆祝之宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来是为了告诉各位一则预言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.27,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了来宣告死亡 夺走一切的希望而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.61,0:16:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了 悲哀土地的后裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等的土地将世代受到谄咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王国跟军队都被毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.42,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从魔法师手中逃脱出来的只有公主跟一对仆人夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个诡异的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望尽快穿越啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 我们先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今只能等待枯萎 真是朵可怜的玫瑰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有水 应该就会娇艳欲滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.82,0:17:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想把你种在王城的庭园 然而如今我却没有半寸土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅弃你而去的我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主脑确认 位置西南方两公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫幻兽群正往东南方散开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敌方防御线之后 就进行PBE搬运作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主流下来的眼泪 渗入了枯萎玫瑰的根部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时神奇的事情发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.89,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你这么不幸 竟然还为毁灭的我叹息而流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个温柔的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人是地上的至宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE开始准备启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次 开始准备启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进行启动准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人无法以剑打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被你拯救生命的人 我是你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE活性化成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等不可能打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即是恐怖、我即是憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起唱和吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不憎恨也不畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块土地的后裔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.92,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能克服恐怖跟憎恨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.09,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的畏惧将会成为憎恨\N我的憎恨将会变成恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我不憎恨也不畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战成功 主脑消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒气浓度急速下降中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始回收 HWT归队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纪、真纪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(剧终)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信 田边太走运了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有这种事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卤马铃薯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话 是你母亲打来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都烧光了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险能不能给付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那我挂电话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 心情不要太低落喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.14,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福 幸福到感觉好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里所有人都没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.12,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE启动辅佐也平安结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能扮演公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.19,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我人生最棒的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是田边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的田边回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.22,0:21:47.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.20,0:21:59.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.45,0:22:05.75,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.52,0:22:11.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我将其收集起来 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.43,0:22:19.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}没人知道我将前往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的风描绘着我的轨迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.07,0:22:31.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}随着时代变动的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.81,0:22:37.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.98,0:22:44.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱紧这相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.42,0:22:53.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}走吧 一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:23:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在绝望的状态下赌上生命 跟幻兽作战的濑户口跟速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面前竟然出现了一位美少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回的高机动幻想 爱情猎人\N敬请期待！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡扯啦
